Mutant with ability to
transform herself to anyone.

54
00:11:35,321 --> 00:11:36,299
Mystique.

55
00:11:37,719 --> 00:11:38,964
I knew her as Raven.

56
00:11:39,766 --> 00:11:42,462
We met when we were children
grew up together.

57
