it gave them the key they needed

72
00:12:37,774 --> 00:12:41,835
to create weapons that could
adapt to any mutant power.

73
00:12:42,348 --> 00:12:44,029
And in less than 50 years

74
00:12:44,201 --> 00:12:49,225
the machines that have destroyed so
many of our kind were created.

75
00:12:50,361 --> 00:12:53,830
But it all started that day in 1973

76
00:12:54,478 --> 00:12:56,299
the day she first killed

77
00:12:56,499 --> 00:12:59,688
