Then we can stop the sentinels
from ever being born.

82
00:13:12,177 --> 00:13:15,021
And end this war
before it ever begins.

83
00:13:19,464 --> 00:13:21,863
I can send someone back a couple of weeks.

84
00:13:23,207 --> 00:13:26,967
