102
00:14:59,397 --> 00:15:01,332
Patience is my strongest suit.

103
00:15:02,198 --> 00:15:03,645
You'll need me as well.

104
00:15:04,001 --> 00:15:04,462
What?

105
00:15:04,629 --> 00:15:06,979
After Mystique left Charles
she came with me

106
00:15:07,053 --> 00:15:09,150
and I set her on a dangerous path.

107
00:15:11,083 --> 00:15:11,883
Darker path.

108
00:15:12,083 --> 00:15:14,681
It's going to take the
two of us side by side

109
00:15:14,681 --> 00:15:17,189
at a time when we couldn't
be further apart.

110
00:15:21,085 --> 00:15:21,911
Great.

111
00:15:23,339 --> 00:15:24,384
So where do I find you?

112
00:15:25,149 --> 00:15:26,329
Well..It's complicated.

113
00:15:29,902 --> 00:15:33,526
Basically your body will go to sleep
while your mind travels back in time.

114
00:15:34,004 --> 00:15:37,293
As long as you back there past and present
will continue to co-exist.

115
00:15:38,943 --> 00:15:40,169
But once you wake up....

116
00:15:41,596 --> 00:15:44,162
.. Whatever you've done will
take hold and become history.

117
00:15:44,557 --> 00:15:47,081
And for the rest of us that will
be the only history that we know.

118
00:15:47,289 --> 00:15:50,108
That will be like
last 50 years never happened.

119
00:15:51,352 --> 00:15:53,579
This world
this war.

120
