124
00:16:04,772 --> 00:16:07,519
If your mind gets rocky
it will harder for me to hold you.

125
00:16:07,554 --> 00:16:09,814
You could start to slip
between past and future.

126
00:16:09,867 --> 00:16:11,736
What if I need to get a little rocky ?

127
00:16:13,093 --> 00:16:14,303
Think peaceful thoughts.

128
00:16:14,750 --> 00:16:15,782
Peaceful thoughts.

129
00:16:16,057 --> 00:16:17,340
