246
00:25:45,925 --> 00:25:48,646
My war is not over.
The enemy is still out there.

247
00:26:12,123 --> 00:26:12,809
Where did they go?

248
00:26:13,009 --> 00:26:14,245
The 4 privates where did they go?

249
00:26:14,356 --> 00:26:15,662
They were headed towards the Tarmac.

250
00:27:15,226 --> 00:27:16,007
Can I help you?

251
